            "**allow_mist** (default: true)",
            "**created_time**",
            "**id**",
            "**modified_time**",
            "**msp_id**",
            "**msp_logo_url**: logo uploaded by the MSP with advanced tier, only present if provided",
            "**msp_name**: name of the msp the org belongs to",
            "**name**",
            "**orggroup_ids**",
            "**session_expiry** (default: 1440)"
